  <summary date="2020-02-29T20:21:35Z" status="Introduced in House">U.S.-Israel Cybersecurity Center of Excellence Act

This bill directs the Department of State to report to Congress on the potential benefits and impact of establishing a U.S.-Israel Cybersecurity Center of Excellence to leverage the expertise of government, higher education, and private-sector entities in cybersecurity and the protection of critical infrastructure.</summary>
